nodes.text: Morro Spaceport was one of the busiest spaceports in the Bright Jewel sector of the Mid Rim. Located at the terminus of the Path of Coins, the spaceport was the central feature of the city of Worlport on the planet Ord Mantell. It was named after a Corellian colonist named Morro when the planet was first settled by the Galactic Republic.
